---
/**
 * Services — Paul Henney Cremation & Funeral Tributes
 * Burial, cremation, and green burial options with transparent pricing.
 */
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Services | Paul Henney Cremation & Funeral Tributes" activePage="services" description="Burial tributes, traditional and contemporary cremation, and green burial options. Thoughtful services, thoughtfully priced.">

<section class="services-hero">
  <div class="services-hero-inner">
    <span class="services-hero-label">Our Services</span>
    <h1 class="services-hero-title">Honoring Every<br />Life, Every Way</h1>
    <div class="services-hero-line"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="services-intro reveal">
  <div class="container--narrow">
    <p class="intro-text">Whether your family chooses burial or cremation, we create personalized tributes that reflect the life lived. Every service is designed around what made your loved one unique.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="service-section reveal" id="burial">
  <div class="service-section-inner">
    <div class="service-image">
      <img src="/images/987238-funeral-fs-600x450-26.jpg" alt="Floral arrangement" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="service-content">
      <h2>Burial Tributes</h2>
      <p>For most families, burial is the preferred method of disposition. Public funerals with viewing allow family and friends to gather, to grieve, and to say goodbye. Seeing a loved one peacefully at rest can be deeply comforting.</p>
      <p>A well-planned, personalized tribute will cause you to remember, reflect, cry, and even laugh. In the end, the funeral fulfills its original purpose: to honor a life lived and begin the healing process for those left to live on.</p>
      <div class="service-detail">
        <span class="service-detail-label">Packages starting at</span>
        <span class="service-detail-price">$5,640</span>
        <span class="service-detail-note">Includes visitation and casket</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="service-section reverse reveal" id="cremation">
  <div class="service-section-inner">
    <div class="service-image">
      <img src="/images/778156-urnwreathwhiteyellow.jpg" alt="Cremation urn with floral arrangement" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="service-content">
      <h2>Traditional Cremation</h2>
      <p>Many families are unaware of the options available with cremation. After a review of the choices, 70% of cremation families choose to have some type of visitation, gathering, or service to accompany this form of disposition.</p>
      <p>We often hear people say "just cremate me." This unselfish statement is meant to spare the family grief and money. But families need a safe, secure place to express their sympathy and begin the transition to living without their loved one while honoring them one last time.</p>
      <div class="service-offerings">
        <h3>Cremation Options</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Traditional cremation with viewing and service</li>
          <li>Contemporary cremation with memorial gathering</li>
          <li>Direct cremation with private family time</li>
          <li>Green burial tributes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="service-section reveal" id="personalized">
  <div class="service-section-inner">
    <div class="service-image">
      <img src="/images/442122-1-our-services.jpg" alt="Family planning personalized service" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="service-content">
      <h2>Personalized Services</h2>
      <p>Paul and veteran funeral director Marie Wohlgemuth take time to learn about the deceased, their family and friends, and what was important in their life. From there, a personalized and fitting funeral service is designed to help tell the life story of the deceased.</p>
      <div class="service-features">
        <div class="feature">
          <h4>Online Memorials</h4>
          <p>Customized memorials for family and friends to post condolences, share memories, and light candles in honor of your loved one.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h4>Tribute Videos</h4>
          <p>Personal tribute videos that transform your treasured photographs into a video celebration of memories, available on DVD or digital.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h4>Aftercare Services</h4>
          <p>Personal follow-up meetings after the funeral to help with administrative tasks and the transition ahead. Plus a year of daily grief support.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pricing reveal" id="pricing">
  <div class="pricing-inner">
    <h2>Thoughtful Services, Thoughtfully Priced</h2>
    <p class="pricing-text">We understand the importance of cost and promise to create services that fit your needs. There are many factors that influence the selection of a funeral home: reputation, integrity, service, price, and standards of care.</p>
    <p class="pricing-text">If price is your only consideration, we may not be your best choice. If you take everything into consideration, you will find us to be an excellent choice providing excellent value.</p>
    <p class="pricing-quote">The value of our service will always be greater than the price.</p>
    <div class="pricing-cta">
      <a href="tel:4128351312" class="cta-button">Call to discuss options</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="preneed reveal" id="preneed">
  <div class="preneed-inner">
    <div class="preneed-content">
      <h2>Pre-Planning</h2>
      <p>The Henney preneed program quickly became one of the most successful in Southwestern Pennsylvania. Pre-arranging relieves the emotional and financial burden from your family before the time of need.</p>
      <p>Planning ahead gives you the opportunity to make your wishes known, lock in today's prices, and spare your family the difficulty of making decisions during a time of grief.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="cta-link-arrow">Request a free planning guide &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div class="preneed-image">
      <img src="/images/924962-man-female-meeting.jpg" alt="Pre-planning consultation" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .services-hero {
    min-height: 55vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-3xl) var(--space-lg) var(--space-2xl);
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 80%, var(--color-amber-glow), transparent 60%);
  }

  .services-hero-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-amber);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .services-hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: var(--font-size-hero);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 0.95;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .services-hero-line {
    width: 60px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--color-amber);
    margin: var(--space-lg) auto 0;
  }

  /* Intro */
  .services-intro {
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-family: var(--font-display), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 55ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Service sections */
  .service-section {
    padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-lg);
    border-top: 1px solid oklch(1 0 0 / 0.04);
  }

  .service-section-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .service-section-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
    }

    .service-section.reverse .service-section-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
    }

    .service-section.reverse .service-image {
      order: 2;
    }
  }

  .service-image img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    filter: brightness(0.9) sepia(0.1);
  }

  .service-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .service-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  /* Price detail */
  .service-detail {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border: 1px solid oklch(1 0 0 / 0.06);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
  }

  .service-detail-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .service-detail-price {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-display), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-amber);
  }

  .service-detail-note {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  /* Offerings list */
  .service-offerings {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .service-offerings h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: var(--font-size-md);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .service-offerings li {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    padding: 0.4em 0;
    padding-left: 1.2em;
    position: relative;
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
  }

  .service-offerings li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.85em;
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-amber-dim);
  }

  /* Features grid */
  .service-features {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .feature h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-display), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: var(--font-size-md);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-amber);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .feature p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Pricing */
  .pricing {
    padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-lg);
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--color-bg-warm);
  }

  .pricing-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-width-narrow);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .pricing-inner h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .pricing-text {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    max-width: 55ch;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .pricing-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-display), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-amber);
    margin: var(--space-xl) auto;
    max-width: 40ch;
  }

  .pricing-cta {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-display), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    color: var(--color-amber);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-amber-dim);
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-xl);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    transition: background 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: var(--color-amber);
    color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  /* Preneed */
  .preneed {
    padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-lg);
  }

  .preneed-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .preneed-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .preneed-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .preneed-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .cta-link-arrow {
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    color: var(--color-amber);
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .cta-link-arrow:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .preneed-image img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 2;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    filter: brightness(0.9) sepia(0.1);
  }
</style>
